title: URGENT NEED HELP
body:
Where is the 'I do not understand' after I got banned, the way I did was go on task manager and end the the shitty thing

ok thank you

replies.body: I think you're talking about that bit where you need to type "I Agree" after getting some sort of punishment. Alt+F4ing probably isn't going to get you around it, as the client will most likely pop that message right back up each time until you type it in.
